{
  "stem": "4187.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a girl sitting up there minding her own business next to the crack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this Aufseherinnen took her whip and-- --laid into her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She-- well, the screams, I can't tell you, and the blood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she fell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She fell down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the Aufseherinnen person, who's done a good job, walked out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "What had happened was that this girl was drinking coffee out of her mug, and there was a little bit left, and she threw it out this crack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the Aufseherinnen was walking by and saw the coffee being poured out, so she made a note of where it was, she came, found the bunk, and that was the end of the girl.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's another scene that you just cannot-- cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just walked out as if that was good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My work done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let's go and look for the next one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that stands out in my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The other thing that stands out in this particular lager, when the Gypsy-- Gypsy compound was emptied, and that was one night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had heard that something is brewing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't know what was brewing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then one night we woke up with-- I don't know, anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll leave it, woke up-- this unbelievable screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we looked out on our slits, and the Gypsy camp, which was right next door to us, the other side of the barbed wire, on one spot was the Gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were reflectors trained onto the camp from everywhere so that it-- it was like Packer's Cricket Ground-- completely and utterly [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But even that in itself was unbelievably frightening, these huge things, lights coming in.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
